e.: cd Test-blogb#@11.4 create test file: > touch test.txtb#@11.5 checkin test.txt by follow below steps:b#@11.5.1 git add test.txtb#@11.5.2 git commit -m 'checkin test file'b#@11.5.3. git push origin masterp#@    img#@\images\git\5push.png 